QuestData.Title: A Sure Bet
QuestData.Description:
You've made a name for yourself and earned the respect of everyone here, including Au'narim.
You are ready, $p!
Anzio is expecting us at the entrance to the Theater of Pain. You're going to be a champion!

QuestData.RewardText: You have traveled far for this moment.
